
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Folliscan | Hair & Scalp Analysis</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6; color: #333; }
        .container { text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); max-width: 400px; }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; }
        .status { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        button { background: #3498db; color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Folliscan</h1>
        <p class="status">● Site Live & Connected</p>
